<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chat Interface</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #6b88c5, #8dbbf1);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .chat-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 10px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            background: url('stars.png') repeat;
        }
        .message-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .message-container.sent {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }
        .profile img {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .message-container.sent .profile img {
            margin-left: 10px;
            margin-right: 0;
        }
        .message-content {
            max-width: 60%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .sender-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .message {
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 0;
        }
        .message.sent {
            background-color: #ffd600;
            color: #000;
        }
        .message.received {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            color: #000;
        }
        .timestamp.sent {
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 5px;
            align-self: flex-start;
            position: relative;
            left: -65px;
        }
        .timestamp {
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 5px;
            align-self: flex-end;
            position: relative;
            left: 65px;
            bottom: 19px;
        }
        .input-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #f8f8f8;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
        .input-container input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            margin-right: 10px;
            border-radius: 0;
        }
        .input-container button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 0;
        }
        .input-container button:hover {
            background-color: #555;
        }
        .icon {
            margin-right: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
